00:48:04,673 --> 00:48:06,842
He should've been arrested in the courtroom,

793
00:48:06,925 --> 00:48:08,427
but he'll end up in jail soon.

794
00:48:08,510 --> 00:48:09,344
-Yes! -Nice!

